OL,4,Ccrash appears in court
OL,6,FIt had been sailing from Grangemouth
OL,7,Fin Scotland to Rotterdam in the
OL,8,FNetherlands.
OL,10,FAll 23 people on board the Stena
OL,11,FImmaculate were rescued, while 13 of
OL,12,Fthe 14 on board the Solong were
OL,13,Fbrought to safety.
OL,15,FThe missing member of the Solong crew
OL,16,Fis believed to be dead. He has been
OL,17,Fnamed by the Crown Prosecution service
OL,18,Fas 38-year-old Filipino national Mark
OL,19,FAngelo Pernia.
