OL,6,FA statement from the Crown Prosecution
OL,7,Fservice said: "Extensive searches were
OL,8,Fcarried out by HM Coastguard to locate
OL,9,Fthe missing crew member, now presumed
OL,10,Fdeceased.
OL,12,F"The family are being supported by
OL,13,Fspecialist trained officers and our
OL,14,Fthoughts remain with them at this
OL,15,Fdifficult time."
OL,17,FAt Hull Magistrates Court no
OL,18,Fapplication for bail was put forward
OL,19,Fand Motin was remanded in custody by
OL,20,Fdeputy chief magistrate Tan Ikram, who
OL,21,Fappeared by video link.
